variables.name: LAST_TIME_USED
variables.comment:
* The last time (in milliseconds) this {@link Data} was used. * @deprecated Contacts affinity information is no longer supported as of * Android version {@link android.os.Build.VERSION_CODES#Q}. * This column always contains 0. * *

Caution: If you publish your app to the Google Play Store, * this field is obsolete, regardless of Android version. For more information, see the * Contacts Provider * page.

variables.name: TIMES_USED
variables.comment:
* The number of times the referenced {@link Data} has been used. * @deprecated Contacts affinity information is no longer supported as of * Android version {@link android.os.Build.VERSION_CODES#Q}. * This column always contains 0. * *

Caution: If you publish your app to the Google Play Store, * this field is obsolete, regardless of Android version. For more information, see the * Contacts Provider * page.

variables.comment:
* @hide
         * Low res version.  Same as {@link #LAST_TIME_USED} but use it in CP2 for clarification.
